RELEASE INSTRUCTIONS - 2.0
These are the steps I followed to output Percolator release 2.0



0. BEFORE YOU START
  [$ git clone git@github.com:percolator/percolator.git]
  CMakeLists.txt and src/converters/CMakeLists.txt: set(CPACK_PACKAGE_VERSION_MAJOR "2"), set(CPACK_PACKAGE_VERSION_MINOR "0")
  build and install in some temporary location and make test


1. PERCOLATOR 64bit
  CMakeLists.txt: set(TARGET_ARCH "amd64")
  $ ./install/get_packages_ubuntu.sh
  $ cd /tmp/percolatorBuild
  $ cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE="Release" -DGOOGLE_TEST="TRUE" -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH="/tmp/xsd-3.3.0-x86_64-linux-gnu;/tmp/gtest-1.5.0" -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX="/usr" /tmp/percolator
  $ make -j8
  $ make package
  $ make package_source

  Output:
  percolator-v2_0-linux-amd64.deb 		percolator + qvality 64bit debian
  percolator-v2_0-linux-amd64.rpm 		percolator + qvality 64bit redhat
  percolator-v2_0-src.tar.gz 			percolator + qvality sources


2. CONVERTERS 64bit
  src/converters/CMakeLists.txt: set(CPACK_PACKAGE_VERSION_MAJOR "2"), set(CPACK_PACKAGE_VERSION_MINOR "0"), set(TARGET_ARCH "amd64")
  [$ ./src/converters/install/get_packages_ubuntu.sh]
  $ cd /tmp/percolator-convertersBuild
  $ cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE="Release" -DGOOGLE_TEST="TRUE" -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH="/tmp/xsd-3.3.0-x86_64-linux-gnu;/tmp/gtest-1.5.0" -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX="/usr" /tmp/percolator/src/converters
  $ make -j8
  $ make package
  $ make package_source

  Output:
  percolator-converters-v2_0-linux-amd64.deb 		sqt2pin + mzidentml2pin 64bit debian
  percolator-converters-v2_0-linux-amd64.rpm 		sqt2pin + mzidentml2pin 64bit redhat
  percolator-converters-v2_0-src.tar.gz 		sqt2pin + mzidentml2pin sources



3. PERCOLATOR 32bit
  CMakeLists.txt: set(TARGET_ARCH "i386")
  hack ./install/get_packages_ubuntu.sh so that it downloads xsd in its 32 bits version.
  repeat point 1 above

  Output:
  percolator-v2_0-linux-i386.deb 		percolator + qvality 32bit debian
  percolator-v2_0-linux-i386.rpm 		percolator + qvality 32bit redhat



4. CONVERTERS 32bit
  CMakeLists.txt: set(TARGET_ARCH "i386")
  [hack ./src/converters/install/get_packages_ubuntu.sh so that it downloads xsd in its 32 bits version.]
  repeat point 3 above

  Output:
  percolator-converters-v2_0-linux-i386.deb 		2pin + mzidentml2pin 32bit debian
  percolator-converters-v2_0-linux-i386.rpm 		2pin + mzidentml2pin 32bit redhat



5. WIN EXECUTABLES
  to be run from an appropriately configured machine: 
  $ ssh [someuser]@dirac.dbb.su.se
  $ ssh -l root -p 2222 localhost
  $ git clone git://github.com/percolator/percolator.git
  $ cd percolator
  $ git checkout rel-2-0
  $ ./install/windows_percolator.sh
  to get it out of the virtual machine:
  $ scp -P 2222 root@dirac.dbb.su.se:/tmp/percolatorBuild/percolator-1.16.0-win32.exe ~/Desktop/

  Output:
  percolator-2.0.0-win32.exe 			percolator + qvality + elude win32



6. BRANCH AND TAG
  upload generated files to https://github.com/percolator/percolator/downloads

  $ git branch branch-2-0
  $ git checkout branch-2-0
  $ git push origin branch-2-0
  $ git checkout master
  $ git branch -f branch-2-0 origin/branch-2-0 #track branch
  $ git checkout branch-2-0
  [$ git push origin :branch-2-0 #delete remote branch if you got it wrong]
  [$ git branch -d branch-2-0 #delete local]

  $ git tag -m 'Setting the rel-2-0 tag' rel-2-0 [commit_hash]
  $ git push --tags
  [$ git push origin :refs/tags/xml-1-1 #delete remote]
  [$ git tag -d xml-1-1 #delete local]



